    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly fixer-upper? This vehicle is ready for some serious TLC! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or a hobbyist to bring it back to life. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own today!",
