      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for someone looking for a major project or a source for spare parts. The engine currently requires significant work to be roadworthy, and the transmission exhibits slipping. Externally, the car shows its age with several large dents, significant rust on the rocker panels, and clear coat failure across the hood and roof. The interior has tears in the upholstery and some non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly 'as-is,' and towing will be required upon purchase.",
